author: CNET
description: This is not your usual speakerphone. Insta360 recently released a professional speakerphone packed with AI to help you with recording meetings, podcasts and more. It features an 8-mic 3D array, AI noise reduction, adaptive beam forming, 32GB of storage and more. The standard bundle starts at $300 for the device and there are subscription plans so you can have more features and more minutes of AI transcription. Unbox it with us🎙️ #insta360 #insta360wave #ai #speakerphone #aitranscription
title: Unboxing the $300 Insta360 Wave AI Speakerphone
